ITV Tour De France 2012 Stage 16 Highlights PDTV x264 AAC

Presented by Gary Imlach, Chris Boardman and Ned Boulting. Commentary: Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen. Stage 16 highlights, Pau to Bagneres-de-Luchon. The first of two gruelling mountains stages through the energy-sapping Pyrenees. A day of spectacular scenery for the spectators, and non-stop suffering for the riders. Today they face the classic route over the Aubisque, Tourmalet, Aspin and Peyresourde.
